  3. Critic agent reviews facts 螕氓脝 updates confidence scores
  4. Reflection engine compresses memory via 0G Compute inference
  5. Final snapshot archived to 0G Storage Log permanently
  6. Restart with same SWARM_ID 螕脟枚 swarm resumes from memory

